{
  "page": "Feature quote/222",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“These little wars are no more than a scuffle of children before what is to come. The <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Other\" title=\"Great Other\">one whose name may not be spoken</a> is marshaling his power, <a href=\"/index.php/Davos_Seaworth\" title=\"Davos Seaworth\">Davos Seaworth</a>, a power fell and evil and strong beyond measure. Soon comes the cold, and the <a href=\"/index.php/Long_Night\" title=\"Long Night\">night that never ends</a>. Unless true men find the courage to fight it. Men whose hearts are fire.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Melisandre\" title=\"Melisandre\">Melisandre</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_36\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 36\">Chapter 36</a>, Davos IV.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260406183635\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.010 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.010 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 95/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 303/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 524/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    6.260      1 -total\n100.00%    6.260      1 Template:Ref\n 62.88%    3.936 